00:54.388 --> 00:56.265
<i>O Yodelers, come yodel ♪</i>

00:56.265 --> 00:58.142
<i>O children, come sing ♪</i>

00:58.142 --> 01:03.439
<i>♪ High up on these mountains,
you hear everything ♪</i>

01:03.439 --> 01:05.733
Yay!

01:10.112 --> 01:12.031
The end.

01:12.031 --> 01:14.366
There are seven more pages, Mama.

01:14.366 --> 01:19.038
Gerhilde, what did we say
about calling me that?

01:19.038 --> 01:20.372
Fine... Governess.

01:20.372 --> 01:25.419
