he hired you because he's a...

01:38.933 --> 01:41.769
..."tit man more than
an ass man."

01:43.187 --> 01:46.065
Gerhilde, please go
the fuck to sleep.

01:49.860 --> 01:52.363
I love you, Governess.

01:57.117 --> 02:00.663
And I you, child.

02:14.093 --> 02:15.928
Good night, Mama.

02:23.769 --> 02:25.104
Sir?

02:25.104 --> 02:26.313
Because
my stories

02:26.313 --> 02:28.315
don't have happy
endings any longer.

02:29.358 --> 02:32.152
That's why their papa
tells them stories no more.

02:34.864 --> 02:37.741
It is an honor to meet you.

02:38.868 --> 02:40.953
Six months is a long time.

02:40.953 --> 02:42.538
I'm happy to be home.

02:42.538 --> 02:45.165
It's been hard on them
since their mother's death.

02:45.165 --> 02:47.251
But I've been told
these past few months with you

02:47.251 --> 02:49.211
have been the happiest time
of their life.

02:49.211 --> 02:50.421
And mine.

02:53.549 --> 02:56.468
I've dreamed of this day
since I came here.

02:57.928 --> 02:59.680
But may I confess something?

02:59.680 --> 03:03.058
I didn't come here
for the children.

03:03.058 --> 03:08.188
I came so that one day I might
get close enough to steal

03:08.188 --> 03:12.318
the heart of the courageous
Rolf Van Klaussen.

03:26.498 --> 03:30.210
And I do mean
steal the heart, Nazi.

03:32.004 --> 03:33.589
Tell me where he is.

03:33.589 --> 03:36.258
I know he's in South America;
tell me how to find him.

03:36.258 --> 03:37.801
I-I don't know what
you're talking about.

03:37.801 --> 03:39.678
You have been overseeing
the export of arms

03:39.678 --> 03:40.679
through São Paulo.

03:40.679 --> 03:42.431
You've been sending them to him.

03:42.431 --> 03:43.849
Now tell me where he is.

03:43.849 --> 03:46.185
Fräulein?

03:49.104 --> 03:50.689
Papa!

03:55.653 --> 03:57.071
No.

04:00.407 --> 04:01.992
I'm sorry.

04:07.331 --> 04:09.124
Mama.

04:09.124 --> 04:11.835
<i>High up on these mountains ♪</i>

04:11.835 --> 04:13.420
<i>You hear everything ♪</i>

05:39.882 --> 05:41.550
You cold?

05:49.808 --> 05:51.477
You look like shit.

05:52.519 --> 05:53.854
Good thing I brought you a gift.

05:53.854 --> 05:55.647
Uh, it's not a good time.

05:56.648 --> 05:58.776
Killed Biff Simpson
two nights ago

05:58.776 --> 06:00.944
in a brothel in Paris.

06:00.944 --> 06:03.280
An old SS haunt.

06:03.280 --> 06:05.199
Shot him through the face.

06:06.200 --> 06:10.287
Uh, if you are here
for confession,

06:10.287 --> 06:12.039
you are at the wrong place.

06:13.290 --> 06:14.541
Confessions are for sins.

06:14.541 --> 06:17.628
He tried to bargain
for his life.

06:17.628 --> 06:19.505
Claimed, if I let him live,

06:19.505 --> 06:22.382
he could bring me
a greater prize.

06:22.382 --> 06:24.927
What?

06:26.095 --> 06:27.096
Hitler.

06:33.685 --> 06:36.438
- You don't really believe...
- He claimed Hitler fled Europe

06:36.438 --> 06:38.857
via ratline and was living
down in South America.

06:38.857 --> 06:41.110
- And what proof did he have?
- We met the proof.

06:41.110 --> 06:42.778
The Colonel.

06:44.822 --> 06:46.406
- Bullshit.
- What other woman could rise

06:46.406 --> 06:48.826
- so high in the ranks?
- Eva Braun killed herself

06:48.826 --> 06:50.619
in the Führerbunker in 1945,
as did Adolf Hitler.

06:50.619 --> 06:52.204
How do you know?

06:52.204 --> 06:54.873
- Hitler's dead, Jonah.
- Says who? The Russians?

06:54.873 --> 06:56.708
They found his body
and just simply burned it?

06:56.708 --> 06:58.085
You really believe that?

06:58.085 --> 06:59.711
People believed
Eichmann was dead too,

06:59.711 --> 07:02.172
until Mossad found him
in South America.

07:02.172 --> 07:05.217
Eichmann, Mengele, Stangl,
Wilhelm Zuchs.

07:05.217 --> 07:06.969
Nazis don't just disappear.

07:06.969 --> 07:09.930
They don't simply
kill themselves.

07:15.352 --> 07:16.812
Before he died,
Biff Simpson said,

07:16.812 --> 07:19.898
"All roads lead through Genoa."

07:21.733 --> 07:23.235
Why Genoa?

07:23.235 --> 07:25.195
Didn't make
any sense to me,

07:25.195 --> 07:28.490
and then I realized
that Genoa is where Eichmann

07:28.490 --> 07:29.825
had fled Europe.

07:29.825 --> 07:33.662
Josef Mengele, too, in July '49.

07:33.662 --> 07:35.664
My contact pulled records

07:35.664 --> 07:38.917
showing that the ships
that ran from Genoa

07:38.917 --> 07:42.421
to Buenos Aires were charted
by a German steel conglomerate

07:42.421 --> 07:44.131
called Essen Industries.

07:44.131 --> 07:48.552
Turns out on April 29, 1945,
Essen Industries also chartered

07:48.552 --> 07:51.430
a ship from Genoa
to Buenos Aires.

07:51.430 --> 07:53.932
Hitler and Eva committed
suicide on the 30th.

07:53.932 --> 07:55.851
What, you think
they were on the ship?

07:55.851 --> 07:57.644
Among the names were
two crewmembers never before

07:57.644 --> 07:59.521
listed on any manifest:

07:59.521 --> 08:01.106
Erik Tolmann
and Frida Tolmann.

08:01.106 --> 08:04.818
Essen Industries' founder
is a man named Klaus Rhinehart.

08:04.818 --> 08:07.070
The Nazi financier.

08:07.070 --> 08:09.698
Now, he is a free man
living in, of all places...

08:10.741 --> 08:12.701
Buenos Aires.

08:12.701 --> 08:14.578
He runs Argentina's
steel industry.

08:17.289 --> 08:20.709
I can charter a plane,
fly us down there undetected.

08:21.835 --> 08:24.004
We find Klaus Rhinehart,
we find Hitler.

08:26.089 --> 08:27.716
We have to tell the Feds.

08:27.716 --> 08:29.134
Aw, fuck. Come on.

08:29.134 --> 08:31.887
What is... what has going to
the Feds ever got you?

08:31.887 --> 08:34.806
A fucking gag order to keep
quiet about Biff Simpson?

08:34.806 --> 08:38.101
A not guilty verdict
for Bishop Prentz?

08:42.564 --> 08:44.733
Why are you here, Jonah? Why me?

08:49.571 --> 08:52.783
Because I can't
do this alone, and...

08:55.619 --> 08:59.831
...I know that you're the only
one that might believe me.

09:08.882 --> 09:10.801
Well, you're in over your head.

09:10.801 --> 09:12.511
Why did you call me?

09:12.511 --> 09:14.846
Why did you call me
when you lost the Prentz case?

09:14.846 --> 09:16.306
Tell me, why?

09:16.306 --> 09:17.891
Maybe it's because you realized

09:17.891 --> 09:20.269
that justice is a privilege
reserved for the few.

09:20.269 --> 09:21.728
And maybe...

09:22.729 --> 09:25.482
...you were looking
for another path.

09:25.482 --> 09:27.776
We find Hitler...

09:28.819 --> 09:30.028
