we have become...

09:35.367 --> 09:37.160
...will have been worth it.

09:38.328 --> 09:39.746
And it can finally be over.

09:49.840 --> 09:52.467
I thought you would understand.

10:00.684 --> 10:01.685
I'm in.

10:05.522 --> 10:07.733
But we can't do it alone,
so where are your friends?

10:09.192 --> 10:12.195
Uh, we're not exactly
on speaking terms.

10:13.530 --> 10:15.324
Then I'll do the talking.

